---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NavPill from '../components/NavPill.astro';

const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric',
});
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What I'm currently focused on.">
  <NavPill />
  <div class="container">
    <article class="now">
      <header class="now__header">
        <h1 class="now__title">Now</h1>
        <p class="now__updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="now__content">
        <p>
          I'm back to having a little too many main objectives at once, but this time with better focus on what truly matters to me.
          I truly believe that I have what it takes to fully actualize myself and at this point it is to continue dismantling any barriers stopping me.

        </p>
        <p>
          Unfortunately, it requires me to go through a lot of emotional conflict from my parents and my own old identity trying to keep me in stasis.
        </p>
        <p>
          I want to try living in Japan. It seems that so many things I enjoy are from there and I want to figure out the core reason why.
          The difficulty to pursue this seems very high, but my mindset has developed over the past few years to where I am accepting that it takes commitment and drive to make anything happen.
        </p>
        <p>
          In the mean time while I keep progressing towards that goal, I am doing my best to focus on building stuff I find meaningful or plainly enjoyable.
          Playing around with vibe coding to make this site and the Usogui archive has been a lot of fun recently.
          </p>
          <p>
            To end things off, I want to let myself know that I need to follow where my core being leads me and to slowly remove the habits that don't help me become who I want to be.
          </p>
      </div>

      <footer class="now__footer">
        <p class="now__note">
          surely future me will figure it out soon
        </p>
        <a href="/now/archive" class="now__archive-link">
          View past "now" entries &rarr;
        </a>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .now {
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-bottom: 80px; /* Space for floating nav */
  }

  .now__header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: var(--border-thick) solid var(--color-gold-dim);
  }

  .now__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    text-shadow:
      0 0 30px rgba(255, 229, 44, 0.4),
      0 0 60px rgba(255, 229, 44, 0.2);
  }

  .now__updated {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .now__content {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .now__content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .now__content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .now__footer {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: var(--border-thin) dashed var(--color-border);
  }

  .now__note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .now__note a {
    color: var(--color-gold-orange);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .now__note a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
  }

  .now__archive-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-label);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .now__archive-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-orange);
  }
</style>
